### Projects

1. Setup Bluehost - student profile page

2. Page Template - includes and render function

3. Page View - render page function with template

4. Test Page - iframe and validator

5. Document Page - markdown formatter

6. Forms Input - testing checklist form

7. Table Formatter - project page index

8. Database Records - notes with add, list

9. Notes App - CRUD views

10. Music Manager - Records: title, description, buy, listen, artwork

11. Slide Shows - notes and slide show

12. Brain - multiple apps: Documents, Notes, Music, Slides, Contacts

13. Wiki - users create articles and comments

14. Photo Gallery - upload images

15. Grand Finale - blog

